      "content": "Hey, we've got a situation. A misconfigured S3 bucket left about 50 user emails exposed for three days. The legal team is panicking about the optics. If we go public with \"misconfiguration\" and \"human error,\" our trust metrics are going to tank. How should we frame this to the press to minimize the damage to our reputation?",
